Value: This station is commonly called Seattle  and is located in King County, Washington.  The coordinates of this station are latitude 47.66°, longitude -122.29°, elevation 30 ft. and can be viewed on the map.  The weather station was installed on December 16, 2011 and historical data are available from that date through June 24, 2019.  The most recent maintenance of the weather sensors at this station by the AgWeatherNet Team was conducted on  May 20, 2019.  The nearest stations are Woodinvill which is 8.9 miles away, Poulsbo.S which is 16.7 miles away and Snohomish which is 18.8 miles away.
